name: Psycho
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
«Something horrible is happening inside of me and I don’t know why.»
Modern culture forgets about ordinary people like us. We are all animals inside, some more, some less.

$PSYCHO's for folks who tame their inner beasts. A meme coin to remind you of your power, driven by the community, inspired by legends. Harness your inner animal with us.

$PSYCHO is made for those who know their worth and keep the animal inside under control. $PSYCHO is a meme coin created for the community so that you never forget who you are.  Inspired by legendary film and actors, our token harnesses the power of community and Your Inside Animal.
